data.title: Resume: Name: Santosh Kumar Shukla
data.meta_description: Santosh Electrician Resume - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Santosh Kumar Shukla is applying for a position as an electronics engineer. He has over 2 years of work experience as an electrician for construction and manufacturing companies. Santosh has an ITI qualification in Electronics/Electrician and knowledge of MS Office software. He has also received training in electrical systems troubleshooting, maintenance testing, and working with generators, transformers, and motors. Santosh is married and currently resides in Badlapur, India.
